Regression:  log(Y) = α₅ + β₅ · log(X) + ε   [Version 4: OLS with constant on log prices]

Run in BOTH directions on 5-year data. For each direction:
  OLS → residuals → adfuller(residuals, autolag='AIC') → p-value
